買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T01:40:12.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T01:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係依排3.6成日冇貨 試左幾款都唔及得用3.6 creamy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"點拎返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日試呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蜂蜜味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oM0KR7V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoM0KR7V.png&h=8d73df4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d1051b81c3a51c4d8e650382f230e40094005e6","tid":2242420,"uid":299187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6f9dbf1f0049633edebf6ca7ed1dd9158468832","tid":2242420,"uid":118146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa8b473e0217974ecb08b69d70ea70901de6fdf2","tid":2242420,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af69252ba7d3ce9463da66a305d4097c46e06042","tid":2242420,"uid":118146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"未試過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用開壓力煲 煲好啲奶放幾嗰鐘就搞掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係電飯煲應該都可以 原理一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:45:34.000Z","msg":"有冇教學"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T01:39:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thekitchn.com/how-to-make-yogurt-at-home-cooking-lessons-from-the-kitchn-125070?amp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thekitchn.com%2Fhow-to-make-yogurt-at-home-cooking-lessons-from-the-kitchn-125070%3Famp%3D1&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2gy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=b0af8b17\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thekitchn.com/how-to-make-yogurt-at-home-cooking-lessons-from-the-kitchn-125070?amp=1</a><br />\n最後個步驟其實將樽乳酪放係個維持到40度既環境就okay<br />\nstarter可以either買無糖純乳酪或者yogurt粉<br />\n牛奶就盡量用full fat 會creamy啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:38:37.000Z","msg":"用759 JERSEY奶，有4.3% 乳脂<br />\n其他奶多數3點幾%<br />\nSTARTER買一D包裝寫明有LIVE CULTURES嘅原味YOGURT，無糖最好，但影響不大<br />\n一盒奶1L，用2-3湯匙YOGURT就夠<br />\n<br />\n第一步煲奶：煲到微滾 跟住攞凍（用黎殺菌）<br />\n用熱水消毒埋個樽，發酵時唔想繁殖埋其他菌<br />\n<br />\n大概攤到38度左右 搵一碗仔奶溝勻左D YOGURT先倒入去攪<br />\n<br />\n最後，香港天氣熱，所以放喺焗爐/ 微波爐過夜都得<br />\n亦有人會擺杯熱水入爐，有人會開著爐燈，有壓力煲/ 蒸焗爐發酵功能都得<br />\n電飯煲都得，睇你驚唔驚整花個煲<br />\n理想發酵溫度35-38C<br />\n你等到佢變半固體就成功架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會聞到酸酸地但好重奶香<br />\n發酵得太耐會變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整完筆起少少留返個種，就有無窮無盡嘅YOGURT食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想濃D/杰身D好似GREEK YOGURT有兩個主要方法：<br />\nSTRAIN或者加兩湯匙全脂奶粉<br />\n我通常加奶粉算（加落熱牛奶），因為STRAIN都要兩粒鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a42bb1a7f7b1cd3d012fbb4414da672ba7bdd9","tid":2242420,"uid":299187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:40:52.000Z","msg":"唔想煩嘅話 有隻西班牙牌子幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}